title: Vercel - Simplifying Your Development with Zero Configuration
abstract:
Struggling with the 1,001 pieces of your JavaScript project? Ready to kickstart your web app journey? Discover the secret of lightning-fast deployments.

Join SSW Software Engineer Tylah Kapa and see your code will go from zero to a live website in seconds.

Tylah will show you the power of Vercel with some real-world applications, a comparison with normal cloud providers…

See you at this interesting talk and explore Vercel's robust tools for personal and professional growth and learn how you can take advantage of this awesome platform.
eventShortDescription:
October .NET User Group:​

Vercel - Simplifying Your Development with Zero Configuration

Struggling with the 1,001 pieces of your JavaScript project? Ready to kickstart your web app journey? Discover the secret of lightning-fast deployments.

Join SSW Software Engineer Tylah Kapa and see your code will go from zero to a live website in seconds.

Tylah will show you the power of Vercel with some real-world applications, a comparison with normal cloud providers…

Come explore Vercel's robust tools for personal and professional growth and learn how you can take advantage of this awesome platform.

--

Join us in person from 5 pm AEST in Brisbane, or 6p m AEDT in Sydney and Melbourne:

SSW Sydney – Watch party 🎦
SSW Melbourne – Watch party 🎦
SSW Brisbane – Live 🔴
